room_title: Escape room "Ka Puka Bunker" by Maui Escape Rooms in Maui
room_description: While hiking a secret jungle trail in the Hawaiian wilderness, you and your companions stumble upon an abandoned World War II artillery battery. Unable to resist, you enter Ka Puka and immediately realize your mistake. A booby trap seals Ka Puka and activates the self-destruct mechanism.
